name: Swarna Kshetra Farm
description: Swarna Kshetra Farm is a lush and fertile agricultural land located in the serene outskirts of Mysuru. This farm is ideal for organic farming, with a natural water source and fertile soil. The property boasts a drip irrigation system and a farmhouse for storing equipment and produce. Its proximity to local markets makes it a lucrative option for farmers focusing on sustainable agriculture.
